  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large paella pan or skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced chicken and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the paprika, garlic powder, onion powder, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the chicken broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, uncovered, for 10 minutes.",
